text: Sandrine Vaucher (born 20 August 1971) is a Swiss freestyle skier. She competed at the 1994 Winter Olympics in Lillehammer, in women's moguls. == References == == External links == * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Switzerland Category:Freestyle skiers at the 1994 Winter Olympics
